ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] Digest Number 162
ygData.msgSnippet: I thought I checked that before
ygData.messageBody:
<< Blackened Iron is nice to look at however.. Banded is a much better choice
for a rangers standard issue under level 25. >>

I thought I checked that before I switched and got more hp with the blackened
than the banded (only checked pieces individually). I still have my
banded-put it on another of my characters, so I guess I could switch back.

Sure they have
one less ac as the banded, however they can kick for magic.. that always
comes in handy. =)

Especially if you want to kick a willowwisp to death!

Panolasi, lvl 10 half-elf ranger
Lany's T'Vyll
